OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fspreading southeast this morning.
OL,7,FBecoming drier and eventually brighter
OL,8,Ffrom the northwest this afternoon with
OL,9,Fthe odd shower. Mild this morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will see a few
OL,12,Fshowers. Then the rest of the night
OL,13,Fwill be mainly dry with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud. Cold with some frost.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FDry in the morning before
OL,17,Foutbreaks of rain spread east across
OL,18,Fall parts in the afternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
