OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Friday with some showery rain.
OL,7,FCloudy on Saturday with rain, heavy at
OL,8,Ftimes, spreading east. Cold and bright
OL,9,Fon Sunday with blustery showers.
